and turn you over to Bumpy.

817
01:17:10,920 --> 01:17:13,480
Change your mind, you can walk right now.

818
01:17:14,640 --> 01:17:17,473
You try to take the girl or me along,
you're dead.

819
01:17:17,760 --> 01:17:20,718
