to get me?

820
01:17:21,000 --> 01:17:22,194
That's right.

821
01:17:27,560 --> 01:17:31,235
I halfway believe you. But, you're my ace,
so I got to call you.

822
01:17:44,440 --> 01:17:47,591
The only thing that's keeping you alive
right now is...

823
01:17:47,720 --> 01:17:50,871
